# Style Guide

## Main Colors
- Night Black: #0A0A0A
- Blood Red: #8B0000
- Vampiric Silver: #C0C0C0
- UV Blue: #1E90FF
- Ancient Gold: #DAA520

## Typography
- Main Font: 'Blade Runner Movie Font', sans-serif
- Secondary Font: 'Gothic', sans-serif
- Headings: 'Vampire Wars', display

## Components

### Buttons
- Primary style: Blood Red with metallic border
- Hover: UV glow pulse effect
- Disabled: Reduced opacity with gray effect

### Cards
- Background: Night Black gradient
- Border: Vampiric Silver with metallic effect
- Hover: Soft red glow

### Modals
- Overlay: Black with 85% opacity
- Border: Metallic effect with Vampiric Silver
- Animation: Fade in with mist effect

## Animations
- Transitions: 300ms ease-in-out
- Hover effects: 200ms
- Page transitions: Fade with blood drip effect

## Layouts
- Dark mode by default
- Fluid elements
- 12-column grid system
- Base spacing: 8px

## Media
- Images with grain effect
- Videos with dark overlay
- Monochromatic style icons

